Package com.qualcomm.robotcore Description

RobotCore library. Contains event loops, socket communication, hardware abstractions, utility methods, and more.

For gamepad information see Gamepad.

To create a custom event loop, see EventLoop.

For information about working with hardware controllers (e.g. servo, motor), see com.qualcomm.robotcore.hardware
